### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/products

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1

### Get non-existent product (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/999

### Create product - Orange
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "3",
  "name": "orange",
  "quantity": 8,
  "price": 12
}

### Create product - Grape
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "4",
  "name": "grape",
  "quantity": 15,
  "price": 25
}

### Create product - Mango
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "5",
  "name": "mango",
  "quantity": 12,
  "price": 30
}

### Create product with duplicate ID (should return 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "1",
  "name": "duplicate banana",
  "quantity": 5,
  "price": 10
}

### Create product with missing fields (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "6",
  "name": "pear"
}

### Update product - Change quantity
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 20
}

### Update product - Change name and price
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "red apple",
  "price": 18
}

### Update product - Full update
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "yellow banana",
  "quantity": 25,
  "price": 20
}

### Update non-existent product (should return 404)
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ghost product"
}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/3

### Delete non-existent product (should return 404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/999

### Get all products (final list)
GET http://localhost:3000/products

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000/
